   Operational Recovery Planning
     * Policies for Operational Recovery Planning (Proposed)
       Outlines the background, timing and three tier requirements for
       ORPs.
     * Procedures for the Development of Operational Recovery Plans
       (Proposed)
       Provides structure, documentation and tools for the development of
       ORPs.
     * Handbook for the Review of Operational Recovery Plans (Proposed)
       Provides direction and tools for the evaluation of ORPs to ensure
       these documents protect the State's IT resources from unacceptable
       risk of interruption.

   CIO Operational Recovery Planning Steering Committee

   We are encouraging the creation of a self-governing Operational
   Recovery Planning CIO Steering Committee to provide guidance to DOIT in
   making good choices related to statewide recovery efforts. If you are
   interested in serving on this committee, please contact Rebecca
   Harrigan at (916) 445-5098 or via e-mail bharrigan@doit.ca.gov.

